---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Hizmetlerimiz - Türkel Global Stands"
  description="Özel dekor stant, standart stant, premium modüler, premium ahşap, milli katılım stant, podyum üretimi ve özel tasarım hizmetlerimiz."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-section-lg bg-navy text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center animate-on-scroll">
        <h1 class="text-h2 font-hanken font-medium mb-6">
          Hizmetlerimiz
        </h1>
        <p class="text-body text-white/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Fuar standı tasarımından üretimine, kurulumundan sökümüne kadar 
          tüm süreçlerde profesyonel hizmet sunuyoruz. Markanızı en güçlü 
          şekilde temsil edecek çözümler üretiyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Overview -->
  <section class="py-section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8 px-4 md:px-0">
          <!-- Service 1: Özel Dekor Stant -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-grey/10 animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zM21 5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a4 4 0 004 4h4a2 2 0 002-2V5z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy mb-3 md:mb-4">Özel Dekor Stant</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Markanıza özel tasarlanan, tamamen özgün ve etkileyici stant çözümleri. 
              Her detayı düşünülmüş, yaratıcı tasarımlarla fark yaratın.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body text-grey space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>3D tasarım ve görselleştirme</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Özel malzeme seçimi</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Marka kimliği entegrasyonu</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Profesyonel kurulum hizmeti</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Service 2: Standart Stant -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-grey/10 animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy mb-3 md:mb-4">Standart Stant</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Ekonomik ve pratik çözümler arayan katılımcılar için hazır tasarım 
              seçenekleri. Hızlı ve etkili çözümler.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body text-grey space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Hazır tasarım seçenekleri</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Ekonomik fiyat avantajı</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Hızlı teslimat süresi</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Temel kurulum hizmeti</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Service 3: Premium Modüler -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-grey/10 animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy mb-3 md:mb-4">Premium Modüler</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Yüksek kaliteli modüler sistemlerle hızlı ve esnek çözümler. 
              Farklı fuarlarda yeniden kullanılabilir sistemler.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body text-grey space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Hızlı kurulum ve söküm</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Yeniden kullanılabilir</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Farklı boyutlara uyarlanabilir</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Uzun vadede maliyet etkin</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Service 4: Premium Ahşap -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-grey/10 animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2-2z"></path>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 21l4-7 4 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy mb-3 md:mb-4">Premium Ahşap</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Doğal ahşap malzemelerle üretilen, şık ve prestijli stant çözümleri. 
              Sıcak ve davetkar atmosfer yaratır.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body text-grey space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Doğal ahşap malzemeler</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Prestijli görünüm</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Çevre dostu çözümler</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Özel işçilik detayları</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Service 5: Grup Stant -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-grey/10 animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy mb-3 md:mb-4">Milli Katılım Stant</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Türkiye'nin uluslararası fuarlardaki milli katılım projelerinde 
              koordineli ve güçlü bir imaj yaratmak için özel tasarlanmış çözümler.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body text-grey space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Milli kimlik vurgulu tasarım</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Koordineli katılımcı standları</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Güçlü ülke imajı yaratır</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Uluslararası standartlarda hizmet</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Service 6: Podyum Üretimi ve Kurulumu -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-grey/10 animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 4V2a1 1 0 011-1h8a1 1 0 011 1v2m0 0V3a1 1 0 011 1v4.586l2.707 2.707A1 1 0 0121 12v8a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-8a1 1 0 01.293-.707L6 8.586V4a1 1 0 011-1V2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy mb-3 md:mb-4">Podyum Üretimi ve Kurulumu</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Etkinlik ve fuarlar için profesyonel podyum tasarımı, üretimi ve kurulumu. 
              Güvenli ve estetik çözümler.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body text-grey space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Özel boyut ve tasarım seçenekleri</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Güvenlik standartlarına uygun</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Hızlı kurulum ve söküm</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Profesyonel görünüm</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Service 7: Özel Tasarım -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-grey/10 animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy mb-3 md:mb-4">Siz İsteyin Biz Tasarlayalım</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Hayalinizdeki stant tasarımını gerçeğe dönüştürüyoruz. 
              Sınırsız yaratıcılık ve özel çözümler.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body text-grey space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Tamamen özelleştirilmiş tasarım</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Sınırsız yaratıcılık</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Konsept geliştirme</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Danışmanlık hizmeti</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="py-section-lg bg-cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16 animate-on-scroll px-4 md:px-0">
          <h2 class="section-heading mb-6">
            Çalışma Sürecimiz<span class="text-orange ml-2">/</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-grey max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Profesyonel yaklaşımımızla, projelerinizi baştan sona titizlikle yönetiyoruz.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8 px-4 md:px-0">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-xl">
              1
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">Konsept & Tasarım</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              İhtiyaçlarınızı analiz ederek, markanıza uygun konsept geliştiriyoruz.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-xl">
              2
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">3D Görselleştirme</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              Tasarımınızı 3D modellerle görselleştirerek, onayınıza sunuyoruz.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-xl">
              3
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">Üretim & Kalite</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              Yüksek kalite standartlarında üretim yaparak, her detayı kontrol ediyoruz.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-xl">
              4
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">Kurulum & Destek</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              Profesyonel ekibimizle kurulum yapıyor, fuar boyunca destek sağlıyoruz.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
